nntp2sql - NNTP to SQL ingestor

Build:
  autoreconf -fi
  ./configure --with-postgres
  make
  sudo make install

Usage:
  ./nntp2sql --host HOST --db-type {sqlite|mariadb|mysql|postgres} --db-name NAME --group GROUP [options]

Export HTML:
  --export-html --group NAME --export-html-out file.html
  --export-html --group-list file --export-html-out out/dir

Viewer:
  ./viewer --db-type sqlite data.db
  ./viewer --db-type mysql host,db,user,pass[,port]
  ./viewer --db-type postgres "host=... dbname=... user=... password=..."

Options:
  --ssl --starttls --user --pass --headers-only --limit --progress-width
  --threads --retries --upsert --init-db --create-db --conf --write-conf --log --verbose

Man page:
  Installed as nntp2sql(1) via `make install`.
  View with: `man nntp2sql`
